{"tid":1768063,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"加入黃色經濟圈低消：參與罷工","createTime":"2019-12-03T20:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T03:36:48.000Z","uid":12517,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcd72303c012f3e5e51204180450622e3c8e709","tid":1768063,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:38:47.000Z","msg":"黃店：<br />\n八月五、十月一、十一月十二至十五等等<br />\n無論幾多日都好 總之要有罷過工先叫黃店<br />\n想做黃店未來就一定要參與罷工<br />\n<br />\n非藍：<br />\n遊行派水、捐錢、連農場、出post屌狗等等<br />\n都入觀察名單 最多叫唔係藍<br />\n<br />\n為防人血飯頭 黃店門檻好重要 罷工先係對運動最大既支持"},{"pid":"ff9345d4b9cbb6bf2e3014fa402314346fb7de45","tid":1768063,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef1ce23d47af43a9f535f162dde6f4f7d613f3d3","tid":1768063,"uid":143151,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"有個conflict 係如果所有黃店都罷 變相個日一出街食飯 就要幫襯藍店"},{"pid":"b16de8f607efec37d1735ff908da861dd4ccd787","tid":1768063,"uid":84363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:55:34.000Z","msg":"出post 屌狗都叫唔黃 你有冇做過生意 你出口冇成本 人地有"},{"pid":"62d0fb04d0a035791084f4afce085fc2a1fc2fe6","tid":1768063,"uid":178800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T21:38:13.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n又玩圍爐果套<br />\n照樓主咁計其實得好少間店叫黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使旨意擴大黃圈<br />\n<br />\n打到呢度,睇番標題,樓主都有寫到經濟圈呢三隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都仲咁樣,一係就真傻,一係就五毛分化<br />\n比個機會樓主你解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed711c0cd5c94bb0a0b52c8774b6d7adde13ff29","tid":1768063,"uid":370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef1ce23d47af43a9f535f162dde6f4f7d613f3d3","tid":1768063,"uid":143151,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"有個conflict 係如果所有黃店都罷 變相個日一出街食飯 就要幫襯藍店"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T22:44:59.000Z","msg